19 THE AUCTION;
20 (3) THE NUMBER OF RENEWABLE ENERGY CREDITS PROJECTED TO BE
21 CREATED AS A RESULT OF THE AUCTION; AND
22 (4) ANY OTHER INFORMATION THE ADMINISTRATION AND THE
23 COMMISSION CONSIDER RELEVANT.
