4 structure should look like in order to promote fast–tracked development at the priority
5 energy sites identified in item (1) of this subsection.
6 (c) On or before December 31, 2026, the Program shall report to the Governor
7 and, in accordance with § 2–1257 of the State Government Article, the General Assembly
8 on the results of the study.
